::Prowl::

Prowl walks into the war room behind Iron Raptor, the doubtful look she had 
on her face troubling him. The maximals have been losing morale lately, and 
that was never a good sign.

He looks at those present, which were no one, and then looks at Iron Raptor. 
"I think the meeting ended already," he said, "We should probably get the 
info from someone."
